{"id": "1313689573058154506", "channel_id": "1313384073422704690", "type": 0, "author_id": "1156423870379741244", "author_name": "kong760", "author_bot": false, "content": "怨鎖是直接鎖角色所有技能\n要看艾爾瓦的驅散效果說明才能確認是不是bug", "timestamp": "2024-12-04T02:13:21.389000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1313384073422704690", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "艾爾瓦解除封印問題", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960"]}
{"id": "1313690468583739512", "channel_id": "1313384073422704690", "type": 0, "author_id": "1156423870379741244", "author_name": "kong760", "author_bot": false, "content": "封印指的只有狂氣被封\n所以驅散封印只有驅散封狂 應該是這樣沒錯", "timestamp": "2024-12-04T02:16:54.899000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1313690468386865182", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-12-04-10-16-08-68_6120889c12ac7e9ba4b3ef1f073858ff.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 67922, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1313384073422704690/1313690468386865182/Screenshot_2024-12-04-10-16-08-68_6120889c12ac7e9ba4b3ef1f073858ff.jpg?ex=69cbd756&is=69ca85d6&hm=1d99a642d55d6be7a4fc419d76a1773e26a5c891b65fdc047e7a24c050abec06&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1313384073422704690", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "艾爾瓦解除封印問題", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960"]}
{"id": "1313705699779543153", "channel_id": "1313384073422704690", "type": 0, "author_id": "297715103565086721", "author_name": "_riku_0330_", "author_bot": false, "content": "原來如此\n因為常用的隊沒有能處理封印狀態的，所以主線的時候沒注意到這件事\n這次用了助戰才從艾爾瓦的卡面上看到能夠「驅散所有喚醒體封印狀態」，以及被鎖的卡上面是寫「封印」\n然後怨恨鎖鏈也是寫封印狂氣爆發和指令卡\n所以產生了疑問", "timestamp": "2024-12-04T03:17:26.299000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1313705699594735706", "filename": "Screenshot_20241204_111434.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 11964, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1313384073422704690/1313705699594735706/Screenshot_20241204_111434.jpg?ex=69cbe586&is=69ca9406&hm=9681217ea220735be9cedf46dd1d660af4fa7878f86fa909b98e0408367a8b0e&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1313384073422704690", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "艾爾瓦解除封印問題", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960"]}
